text: Sidney Parvin (12 July 1883 - 25 August 1956) was a British swimmer. He competed in the men's 100 metre backstroke event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1883 births Category:1956 deaths Category:British male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Great Britain Category:Swimmers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
